msgctxt "548"
msgid "Up-to-date Woman"
msgstr "Donna al passo coi tempi"

msgctxt "552"
msgid "Out-of-touch Woman"
msgstr "Donna non al passo con i tempi"

msgctxt "72_Up-to-date Woman"
msgid ""
"Really? You don't watch Princess League? You just have to! Haruka-chan is "
"gonna be huge, you watch! She's got talent and cuteness in spades!"
msgstr ""
"Ma dai? Non guardi la Princess League? Devi proprio! Haruka-chan spaccherà, "
"vedrai! Ha talento e carineria a palate!"

msgctxt "84_Up-to-date Woman"
msgid "I haven't been watching TV much at all."
msgstr "Non ho guardato granché la TV."
